A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104445090%2Cimgsize-36520.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fyou-think-you-can-get-away-with-this-wasim-akram-lashes-out-at-mickey-arthur-for-his-bizarre-comments%2Farticleshow%2F104445114.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Legendary%20fast%20bowler%20Wasim%20Akram%20minced%20no%20words%2C%20after%20Pakistan's%20crushing%207-wicket%20defeat%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20India%20in%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%2C%20while%20lashing%20out%20at%20team%20director%20Mickey%20Arthur%20for%20making%20bizarre%20comments%20after%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20heart-breaking%20loss%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fyou-think-you-can-get-away-with-this-wasim-akram-lashes-out-at-mickey-arthur-for-his-bizarre-comments%2Farticleshow%2F104445114.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Unusual%20Asset%20Of%20Hamas%20Is%20Complicating%20Israel's%20Retaliation%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThough%20Hamas%20is%20no%20match%20for%20the%20technological%20sophistication%20of%20the%20Israeli%20army%2C%20the%20group%20has%20one%20very%20unusual%20asset%3A%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20secret%20subterranean%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Israel%20began%20to%20grasp%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20the%20labyrinth%20in%202014%2C%20it%20has%20spent%20over%20%241%20billion%20developing%20an%20underground%20barrier%20along%20its%2060-kilometer%20border%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20more%20on%20a%20system%20to%20detect%20the%20construction%20of%20new%20tunnels%20-%20measures%20it%20has%20dubbed%20the%20'Iron%20Wall'%20and%20'Iron%20Spade.'%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20defenses%20were%20meant%20to%20make%20its%20territory%20unimpregnable.%20But%20in%20at%20least%20one%20case%2C%20the%20hidden%20passageways%20were%20used%20to%20abet%20the%20cross-border%20attacks%20which%20last%20week%20killed%201%2C200%20people%2C%20supplementing%20incursions%20by%20air%2C%20land%20and%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20Israel%20signals%20an%20imminent%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%2C%20the%20same%20network%20is%20complicating%20its%20military%20retaliation%20-%20not%20least%20because%20Hamas%2C%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20says%20it's%20holding%20Israeli%20hostages%20in%20subterranean%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20as%20one%20layer%20for%20civilians%20and%20then%20another%20layer%20for%20Hamas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jonathan%20Conricus%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20to%20that%20second%20layer%20that%20Hamas%20has%20built.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20underground%20maze%20will%20not%20be%20easy.%20Past%20attempts%20have%20been%20hampered%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20one%20but%20Hamas%20knows%20their%20full%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Israel%20said%20it%20had%20destroyed%20100%20kilometers%20of%20tunnels%20underneath%20Gaza.%20But%20Hamas%20insisted%20it%20had%20a%20network%20of%20500%20kilometers%2C%20of%20which%20only%205%25%20was%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20gain%20the%20edge%20over%20its%20foe%2C%20Israel%20in%202014%20decided%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20sophisticated%20tunnel-detection%20system%20developed%20by%20Israeli%20firms%20Elbit%20Systems%20and%20Rafael%20Advanced%20Defense%20Systems%2C%20the%20two%20contractors%20who%20also%20jointly%20worked%20on%20the%20missile%20defense%20system%20known%20as%20Iron%20Dome.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sensors%20aren't%20foolproof%20as%20they%20can't%20detect%20tunnels%20that%20turn%20and%20get%20confused%20by%20intersections%2C%20according%20to%20research%20by%20the%20Tel%20Aviv-based%20Institute%20for%20National%20Studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20advancing%20technological%20countermeasures%2C%20tunneling%20remains%20a%20very%20effective%20way%20for%20one%20side%20to%20literally%20undermine%20another's%20dominance%20of%20the%20surface%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scott%20Savitz%2C%20a%20military%20expert%20at%20the%20Rand%20Corporation.%20The%20opposing%20side%20%26quot%3Bnever%20knows%20whether%20tunnels%20exist%2C%20how%20many%20there%20are%2C%20or%20where%20they%20are.%20They%20only%20know%20the%20ones%20that%20they%20found.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20for%20years%20has%20made%20use%20of%20the%20tunnels%20under%20the%20densely-populated%20Gaza%20to%20conceal%20weapons%2C%20command%20facilities%20and%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20the%20passageways%20have%20become%20more%20sophisticated%20with%20ventilation%20shafts%20and%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20reach%20a%20depth%20of%2035%20meters%20and%20can%20even%20be%20equipped%20with%20railroad%20tracks%20and%20communication%20rooms%2C%20according%20to%20experts.%20The%20entrance%20to%20them%20often%20lies%20in%20residential%20buildings%20or%20other%20public%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20subterranean%20network%20was%20intended%20mainly%20to%20smuggle%20goods%20and%20weapons%20from%20Egypt%20into%20the%20narrow%20strip%20of%20land%20that%20Israel%20withdrew%20from%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20militants%20also%20used%20it%20for%20cross-border%20raids%2C%20including%20the%20operation%20in%202006%20in%20which%20they%20kidnapped%20Israeli%20soldier%20Gilad%20Shalit%2C%20then%20aged%2019%2C%20killing%20two%20other%20Israeli%20soldiers.%20Shalit%20was%20released%20five%20years%20later%20in%20return%20for%20Israel%20freeing%20more%20than%201%2C000%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20staged%20a%20ground%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20in%202014%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20underground%20labyrinth%2C%20which%20Hamas%20militants%20had%20used%20to%20ambush%20Israeli%20forces%20during%20the%2050-day%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgypt%20also%20clamped%20down%20starting%20about%20a%20decade%20ago%20through%20a%20coordinated%20campaign%20to%20destroy%20the%20tunnels%2C%20including%20by%20flooding%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsing%20robots%20to%20explore%20the%20tunnel%20complex%20can%20reduce%20risks.%20But%2C%20Savitz%20warned%2C%20due%20to%20confined%20spaces%2C%20booby%20traps%20and%20other%20defenses%2C%20and%20defenders'%20greater%20knowledge%20of%20the%20underground%20environment%2C%20Israeli%20troops%20who%20try%20to%20enter%20them%20will%20be%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Ba%20severe%20disadvantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697374500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fnt6qqn0k_israel-military-near-border-afp_625x300_15_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-an-unusual-asset-of-hamas-is-complicating-israels-retaliation-plan-4483438%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20Hamas%20is%20no%20match%20for%20the%20technological%20sophistication%20of%20the%20Israeli%20army%2C%20the%20group%20has%20one%20very%20unusual%20asset%3A%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20secret%20subterranean%20tunnels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-an-unusual-asset-of-hamas-is-complicating-israels-retaliation-plan-4483438%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-an-unusual-asset-of-hamas-is-complicating-israels-retaliatio