20Israeli%20government%2C%20politicians%20from%20countries%20allied%20to%20them%2C%20raging%20against%20Hamas%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20whose%20rocket%20attack%20on%207th%20October%20set%20off%20this%20round%20of%20violence.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20some%20governments%20friendly%20to%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20diaspora%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20other%20folks%2C%20are%20calling%20out%20the%20chronic%20violence%20committed%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20over%20the%20years%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20does%20your%20just-turned-18%20moral%20compass%20'thingy'%20say%3F%20Something%20is%20off%2C%20right%3F%20Here%20is%20Hamas%2C%20and%20the%20IDF%2C%20both%20indulging%20in%20extreme%20violence%2C%20both%20numb%20to%20the%20destruction%20they%20are%20causing%2C%20both%20trying%20to%20explain%20their%20violence%20as%20'just'%20-%20isn't%20there%20actually%20something%20terribly%20wrong%20with%20both%20of%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20mind%2C%20Hamas%20and%20the%20Israeli%20war%20machine%20are%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin%20that%20is%20defined%20by%20one%20word%20-%20violence.%20Both%20are%20practically%20addicted%20to%20violence%2C%20and%20share%20a%20terrible%20worldview%20-%20that%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20world%20can%20only%20be%20addressed%20by%20resorting%20to%20bombings%20and%20killings%2C%20and%20through%20instilling%20fear%20and%20terror%20among%20those%20opposed%20to%20them.%20Both%20see%20the%20human%20cost%2C%20military%20and%20civilian%2C%20as%20acceptable%20collateral%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20surely%2C%20both%20need%20to%20be%20condemned.%20Plain%20and%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20can%20see%20that%20you%20get%20it.%20And%20yet%2C%20amazingly%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20don't.%20The%20really%20worrying%20thing%20is%20that%20many%20of%20those%20who%20don't%20get%20it%2C%20are%20people%20currently%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20world.%20Sample%20this%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20kiss%20the%20hands%20of%20those%20who%20planned%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Zionist%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Iran's%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attacks.%20Iran%2C%20as%20you%20know%2C%20is%20Hamas's%20biggest%20supporter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20great%20liberation%20has%20begun%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20big%20billboard%20in%20Tehran.%20Their%20logic%20is%20simple%2C%20the%20enemy%20of%20my%20enemy%2C%20is%20my%20friend.%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20are%20sworn%20enemies.%20US%20too%2C%20calls%20Iran%20a%20fundamentalist%2C%20regressive%2C%20rogue%20nation.%20More%20about%20this%20in%20a%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20here%20are%20statements%20from%20Israel's%20leaders%20-%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20tweet%2C%20describing%20Hamas%20-%20'They%20are%20savages'.%20Yoav%20Gallant%2C%20Israel's%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20-%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20fighting%20against%20human%20animals%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%207th%20October%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20surprise%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20which%20started%20with%20literally%20firing%20around%205%2C000%20rockets%20into%20the%20country%2C%20which%20killed%20hundreds%2C%20including%20civilians.%20Alongside%2C%20teams%20of%20Hamas%20militia%20crossed%20into%20Israel%2C%20some%20of%20them%20targeting%20civilians.%20Reports%20say%20Hamas%20killed%20260%20Israeli%20youth%20attending%20a%20music%20festival.%20An%20unknown%2C%20but%20large%20number%20of%20Israeli%20citizens%20have%20also%20been%20taken%20hostage%2C%20and%20Hamas%20has%20said%20it%20may%20execute%20one%20hostage%20for%20every%20Israeli%20bombing%2C%20and%20even%20broadcast%20the%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20threat%20wasn't%20inhuman%20enough%2C%20the%20response%20of%20Israel%20Finance%20Minister%20Bezalel%20Smotrich%20is%20almost%20as%20callous%20-%20'We%20can't%20worry%20about%20the%20hostages%20too%20much%2C%20now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20be%20cruel...'.%20This%20sums%20up%20how%20numb%20both%20sides%20are%20to%20violence%2C%20where%20even%20the%20likelihood%20of%20collateral%20deaths%2C%20even%20of%20their%20own%20people%2C%20no%20longer%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20the%20immediate%20picture%2C%20let's%20rewind%20a%20bit%20as%20well.%20Even%20if%20we%20travel%20back%20just%2015%20years%2C%20we%20can%20see%20how%20the%20violence%20has%20been%20constant%2C%20on%20a%20huge%2C%20agonizing%20scale.%20According%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20(OCHA)%2C%20since%202008%2C%206%2C407%20Palestinians%20and%20308%20Israelis%20have%20died%20in%20conflict%20situations.%20Also%20152%2C560%20Palestinians%20and%206%2C307%20Israelis%20injured.%20The%20dead%20include%201%2C440%20Palestinian%20children%2C%20and%2025%20Israeli%20children.https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fdata%2Fcasualties%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%20even%20play%20politics%20over%20these%20numbers.%20Some%20say%20that%20the%20much%20higher%20Palestinian%20casualties%20show%20that%20the%20IDF%20is%20the%20bigger%20perpetrator.%20Some%20point%20back%20at%20Hamas's%20'terror'%20tactics%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20the%20use%20of%20suicide%20bombers.%20But%20to%20my%20mind%2C%20these%20massive%20numbers%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20only%20point%20towards%20blind%20bloodlust.%20How%20can%20both%20sides%20not%20see%20that%20violence%20is%20not%20working%3F%20The%20IDF's%20violence%20is%20not%20making%20the%20lives%20of%20Israelis%20safer.%20Hamas's%20violence%20is%20not%20protecting%20the%20Palestinians%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20far%20from%20calling%20on%20them%20to%20back%20down%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20only%20had%20almost%20unstinted%20support%20from%20their%20respective%20'backers'.%20Israel%20has%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20several%20other%20Western%20nations%20in%20its%20corner%2C%20while%20Hamas%20has%20Iran%20fully%20committed%20to%20its%20cause.%20This%20gives%20both%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20almost%20limitless%20funding%2C%20arms%2C%20and%20logistical%20support.%20Both%20sides%20justify%20their%20violence%20by%20pointing%20at%20the%20other%20-%20Hamas%20points%20at%20Israel's%20systematic%20choking%20of%20all%20economic%20growth%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20particularly%20in%20Gaza.%20You%20will%20repeatedly%20hear%20of%20Gaza%20being%20described%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20'open%20air%20jail'%2C%20as%20access%20into%20and%20out%20of%20Gaza%20has%20been%20controlled%20by%20Israel%20for%20decades%20-%20from%20livelihoods%2C%20to%20food%2C%20to%20medical%20and%20building%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHuman%20rights%20activists%20and%20countries%20supporting%20the%20Palestinians%20say%20that%20the%20anger%20from%20Israel's%20aggression%2C%20from%20the%20choking%20of%20Gaza%2C%20to%20the%20extending%20of%20Israeli%20settlements%20beyond%20agreed%20boundaries%2C%20fuels%20anger%20and%20support%20for%20Hamas.%20Israel%20says%20its%20actions%20are%20'retaliatory'%20and%20it%20is%20Hamas's%20violence%20that%20must%20first%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReligion%20is%20the%20other%20dangerous%20dimension%20and%20for%20long%2C%20many%20have%20made%20it%20a%20Jewish%20vs%20Muslim%20confrontation.%20You%20would%20have%20noticed%20how%20a%20few%20days%20back%20students%20in%20Harvard%20University%2C%20who%20supported%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20were%20called%20out%20as%20'anti-Semites'.%20The%20irony%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20Christian%20supremacists%2C%20who%20are%20in%20fact%20anti-Jewish%20and%20anti-Muslim%20(but%20that's%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20another%20letter%2C%20so..)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20surely%20all%20this%20must%20be%20called%20out.%20We%20can't%20be%20tricked%20into%20a%20'chicken-and-egg'%2C%20or%20a%20'who-started-it'%20debate.%20That%20debate%20will%20never%20end.%20Someone%20will%20take%20you%20back%20to%20the%20Arab-Israeli%201967%20war%2C%20someone%20will%20take%20you%20back%20a%20100%20years%20to%20the%20British%20'promise'%20of%20a%20Jewish%20nation%20in%20Palestine%2C%20someone%20will%20take%20you%20back%20to%20the%20Crusades.%20Ugghh!%20No%2C%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20fall%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20end%20by%20mentioning%20a%20political%20leader%20who%20is%20getting%20it%20right.%20That%20guy%20is%20Hamza%20Yousaf%2C%20the%20First%20Minister%20of%20Scotland%20(essentially%20Scotland's%20PM!).%20Of%20Pakistani%20origin%2C%20he's%20already%20a%20path-breaker%2C%20by%20being%20Scotland's%20first%20South%20Asian%20First%20Minister.%20Yousaf's%20Palestinian%20origin%20father-in-law%20and%20Scottish%20mother-in-law%20are%20currently%20stranded%20in%20Gaza.%20They%20had%20gone%20to%20meet%20an%20ailing%20relative.%20Even%20as%20he%20went%20on%20air%2C%20expressing%20his%20helplessness%20at%20not%20knowing%20if%20they%20were%20safe%2C%20he%20stayed%20away%20from%20taking%20sides.%20At%20a%20prayer%20service%20in%20memory%20of%20a%20Glasgow%20resident%20killed%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20Yousaf%20told%20the%20Jewish%20community%2C%20'Your%20grief%20is%20my%20grief.'%20He%20later%20met%20up%20with%20Palestinians%20and%20categorically%20stated%20that%20the%20loss%20of%20innocent%20lives%20in%20both%20Israel%20and%20Gaza%20cannot%20be%20justified%2C%20and%20called%20for%20the%20opening%20of%20humanitarian%20corridors%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20is%20statesmanship!%20This%20man%20is%20a%20Muslim%2C%20leading%20a%20Western%20power.%20But%20instead%20of%20succumbing%20to%20the%20pressures%20of%20'picking%20a%20side'%2C%20of%20doing%20what%20may%20be%20'politically%20popular'%20in%20Scotland%2C%20he%20came%20out%20squarely%20against%20violence%2C%20in%20any%20form%2C%20being%20practised%20by%20any%20one%2C%20for%20any%20reason.%20Like%20Hamza%20Yousaf%2C%20it%20is%20time%20for%20other%20world%20leaders%2C%20and%20even%20for%20all%20of%20us%20people%20who%20choose%20our%20leaders%2C%20to%20reclaim%20and%20get%20back%20to%20using%20our%20'moral%20compass%20thingy'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20your%20world%20now.%20Become%20a%20'moral%20compass'%20evangelist%20in%20your%20corner%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELove%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPapa%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Rohit%20Khanna%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20commentator%20and%20video%20storyteller.%20He%20has%20been%20Managing%20Editor%20at%20The%20Quint%2C%20Executive%20Producer%20of%20Investigations%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Projects%20at%20CNN-IBN%2C%20and%20is%20a%202-time%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20award%20winner)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697365500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fp8t6qt08_israel-palestine-reuters-_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fuse-your-moral-compass-a-fathers-letter-to-daughter-on-israel-hamas-war-4482942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20forces%20were%20Sunday%20readying%20for%20a%20looming%20Gaza%20ground%20invasion%20aimed%20at%20destroying%20Hamas%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20militant%20group%20that%20unleashed%20the%20bloodiest%20attack%20in%20the%20country's%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fuse-your-moral-compass-a-fathers-letter-to-daughter-on-israel-hamas-war-4482942%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shoaib%20Akhtar%20Responds%20To%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20On%20'Billkoool%20Thanda'%20Post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20geared%20up%20to%20face%20each%20other%20in%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20on%20Saturda