g%3E%20Salman%20Rushdie%2C%20the%20acclaimed%20Indian-born%20novelist%2C%20will%20write%20about%20his%20experience%20of%20surviving%20and%20recovering%20from%20an%20attempted%20assassination%20attempt%C2%A0last%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20new%20memoir%20called%20%3Cem%3EKnife%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EKnife%3A%20Meditations%20After%20an%20Attempted%20Murder%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20will%20be%20published%20April%2016%2C%20according%20to%20his%20publisher%20Penguin%20Random%20House.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20necessary%20book%20for%20me%20to%20write%3A%20a%20way%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20what%20happened%2C%20and%20to%20answer%20violence%20with%20art%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rushdie%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguin.co.uk%2Farticles%2F2023%2F10%2Fsalman-rushdie-knife-publication%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20August%2C%20Rushdie%20was%20stabbed%20repeatedly%20in%20the%20neck%20and%20abdomen%20on%20stage%20at%20the%20Chautauqua%20Institution%20in%20New%20York%20State%20where%20came%20to%20give%20a%20lecture.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsalman-rushdie-middle-east-iran-new-york-2aaf7c8fdc459c664173beb4dc0a9ef5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eattacker%2C%20Hadi%20Matar%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20pleaded%20%E2%80%98not%20guilty%E2%80%99%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsalman-rushdie-new-york-pennsylvania-bcfc72d0c6edbdea38e80809abe395a1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echarges%20of%20assault%20and%20attempted%20murder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attack%20left%20Rushdie%20blind%20in%20one%20eye%20and%20he%20lost%20sense%20in%20some%20of%20his%20fingertips.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSpeaking%20out%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20in%20unforgettable%20detail%2C%20about%20the%20traumatic%20events%20of%20August%2012%2C%202022%2C%20%E2%80%98Knife%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20powerful%2C%20deeply%20personal%2C%20and%20ultimately%20uplifting%20meditation%20on%20life%2C%20loss%2C%20love%2C%20the%20power%20of%20art%2C%20finding%20the%20strength%20to%20keep%20going%20%E2%80%93%20and%20to%20stand%20up%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20press%20release%20published%20by%20Vintage%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20this%20stabbing%2C%20Rushdie%20was%20subjected%20to%20death%20threats%20due%20to%20alleged%20blasphemy%20in%20his%20fourth%20novel%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Satanic%20Verses%3C%2Fem%3E.%20After%20the%20supreme%20leader%20of%20Iran%20Ruhollah%20Khomeini%20issued%20a%20fatwa%20calling%20for%20Rushdie%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%201989%2C%20Rushdie%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsalman-rushdie-stabbing-memoir-694ffbbc6460bb9fd2bf7fa78d7ae197%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espent%20years%20in%20hiding%2C%20living%20in%20isolation%20with%20round-the-clock%20security%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6270878%2Fsalman-rushdie-interview-time100%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterview%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETIME%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20while%20working%20on%20the%20book%2C%20Rushdie%20said%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20very%20slow%20steps%20back%20into%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20intend%20to%20reclaim%20my%20life%20as%20fully%20as%20I%20can%2C%20but%20slowly%20does%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rushdie%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKnife%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20searing%20book%2C%20and%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20power%20of%20words%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20unthinkable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20CEO%20%3C%2Fspan%3E