pics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saakhi%3A%20When%20Media%20Reduces%20War%20to%20a%20Video%20Game%2C%20News%20to%20Some%20Stale%20Jokes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19135234%2FNews-studio.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaakhi%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20about%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%2C%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20period%20of%20lawlessness%2C%20your%20brain%20suddenly%20splits.%20It%20begins%20to%20experience%20time%20in%20two%20dimensions.%20One%20is%20the%20subjective%20time%20driving%20your%20personal%20life%2C%20your%20personal%20ambitions%2C%20dreams%2C%20and%20reflective%20abilities.%20The%20other%20is%20the%20vast%20historical%20time%20as%20experienced%20by%20races%20and%20generations%20before%20you.%20That%20as%20you%20read%20about%20it%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20juggernaut%20at%20once%20ruthless%20and%20uncaring%20of%20individuals%20and%20their%20hopes%20or%20aspirations%20each%20time%20it%20begins%20its%20journey%20on%20some%20path%20planned%20by%20destiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECan%20we%20accept%2C%20as%20media%20persons%2C%20that%20leadership%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20is%20bringing%20forth%20vast%20changes%20in%20all%20spheres%2C%20including%20in%20your%20profession%2C%20making%20you%20feel%20small%2C%20redundant%2C%20and%20full%20of%20self-doubt%3F%20The%20laws%20proliferate%20and%20change%20so%20fast%20that%20every%20one%20of%20us%20suspects%20he%20or%20she%20may%20be%20breaking%20a%20half-understood%20new%20law%20somehow.%20And%20so%20when%20a%20citizen%20we%20know%20to%20be%20totally%20innocent%20of%20the%20charges%20levelled%20against%20him%2Fher%20is%20hauled%20and%20%E2%80%9Cheld%20back%20for%20long%20questioning%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20authorities%2C%20our%20first%20reaction%20is%20to%20wonder%20even%20if%20momentarily%20that%20maybe%20he%20has%20broken%20a%20law%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way.%20Authoritarianism%20feeds%20on%20such%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20doubt%20and%20confusion%20about%20the%20constitution.%20Hence%20the%20proliferation%20of%20decrees%20and%20ordinances%2C%20and%20bills%20being%20passed%20hurriedly%20by%20voice%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20long%20existence%20under%20such%20circumstances%20makes%20the%20people%20docile%20and%20ready%20to%20follow%20the%20new%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20unquestioningly.%20In%202023%2C%20we%20learn%20countries%20earlier%20considered%20%E2%80%98friends%E2%80%99%20must%20now%20be%20seen%20as%20unfriendly%20under%20the%20new%20treaties%20signed%20by%20those%20who%20live%20and%20work%20only%20in%20the%20vast%20time%20not%20available%20to%20us.%20The%20more%20space%20the%20Vast%20Time%20buys%20for%20the%20state%2C%20the%20less%20there%20is%20for%20us%20to%20ponder%20over%20the%20new%20developments.%20We%20accept%20projects%20and%20new%20buildings%20made%20with%20public%20money%20being%20gifted%20personally%20to%20us%20by%20the%20leadership.%20We%20accept%20becoming%20stooges%20to%20superpowers%20we%20see%20shaking%20hands%20and%20giving%20bear%20hugs%20to%20our%20leadership.%20The%20future%20shall%2C%20we%20learn%2C%20no%20longer%20grow%20organically%20out%20of%20our%20known%20historical%20past%20but%20a%20new%20world%20order%2C%20newer%20coalitions%20that%20mandate%20a%20new%20interpretation%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESchools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions%20all%20must%20abandon%20old%20history%20and%20subscribe%20to%20new%20ones%20even%20if%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20sense.%20Our%20subjective%20time%20seems%20to%20have%20ceased%20to%20matter.%20Su