3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20not%20this%20easy%20for%20Rubi%20to%20bring%20home%20the%20bacon.%20Coming%20from%20a%20conservative%20background%2C%20Rubi%20was%20questioned%20for%20her%20capabilities.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20my%20in-laws%20that%20I%20wished%20to%20experiment%20with%20organic%20farming%20on%20our%20land%2C%20they%20would%20mock%20me.%20My%20father-in-law%20questioned%20what%20can%20I%20achieve%20by%20doing%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20she%20managed%20to%20start%20her%20experiment%20with%20one%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20land.%20Sadly%2C%20she%20could%20not%20get%20a%20good%20yield%20for%20the%20initial%202-3%20years.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20year%2C%20our%20yield%20was%20very%20low%20comparatively.%20From%20one%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20land%2C%20we%20would%20get%2012%20quintals%20of%20wheat%20with%20the%20application%20of%20chemicals%20but%20with%20the%20organic%20fertiliser%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20just%20get%20roughly%20eight%20quintals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDetermined%20irrespective%20of%20low%20profits%2C%20Rubi%20continued%20to%20farm%20organically%20and%20utilised%20composts%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejeevamrut%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20liquid%20organic%20fertiliser%20made%20from%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine)%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20and%20vermicompost.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20aware%20that%20initially%2C%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20get%20good%20produce%20as%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20heal%20the%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20years%20of%20toiling%2C%20Rubi%20started%20getting%20good%20produce%20that%20fetched%20her%20a%20double%20income.%20Today%2C%20she%20has%20been%20able%20to%20convert%20the%20entire%2026-acre%20family%20farmland%20into%20a%20profitable%20organic%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20sr