d%20by%20the%20rampant%20littering%20and%20indiscriminate%20disposal%20of%20garbage%2C%20Kandelwal%20started%20the%20%E2%80%98Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%E2%80%99%20campaign%20in%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMaka%20naka%20plastic%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20plastic%E2%80%99%20in%20Konkani%2C%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20official%20language.%20The%20campaign%20involves%20making%20different%20types%20of%20bags%20from%20pre-loved%20fabric%20which%20is%20collected%20through%20collection%20drives%20at%20Sensible%20Earth%20and%20also%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20city%20corporation%20of%20Panaji.%20They%20use%20social%20media%20and%20newspapers%20as%20means%20to%20ask%20citizens%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307217%2Fyobler-platform-sells-preloved-used-baby-products-toys-clothes-bedding-sustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edonate%20pre-loved%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20from%20complaining%20to%20catalysing%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20take%20away%20the%20right%20only%20to%20complain%20and%20start%20doing%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Khandelwal%2C%20a%2059-year-old%20serial%20entrepreneur%2C%20early-stage%20investor%2C%20and%20mentor%20to%20tech%20startups%2C%20who%20has%20a%20rich%20history%20in%20the%20internet%20sector.%20He%20played%20a%20pioneering%20role%20in%20developing%20B2B%20marketplaces%2C%20wireless%20networks%2C%20and%20dynamic%20pricing%20engines.%20His%20noteworthy%20work%20even%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20case%20study%20at%20IMD%20in%20Lausanne.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20738px)%20100vw%2C%20738px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSajiv-Khandelwal-with-school-teachers-during-the-Maka-Naka-Plastic-campaign_11zon-1697030448.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22738%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sanjiv%20Khandelwal%20with%20school%20teachers%20during%20the%20Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%20campaign.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSajiv-Khandelwal-with-school-teachers-during-the-Maka-Naka-Plastic-campaign_11zon-1697030448.jpg%20738w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSajiv-Khandelwal-with-school-teachers-during-the-Maka-Naka-Plastic-campaign_11zon-1697030448-197x300.jpg%20197w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSajiv-Khandelwal-with-school-teachers-during-the-Maka-Naka-Plastic-campaign_11zon-1697030448-500x763.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSajiv-Khandelwal-with-school-teachers-during-the-Maka-Naka-Plastic-campaign_11zon-1697030448-150x229.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332045%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221126%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESanjiv%20Khandelwal%20with%20school%20teachers%20during%20the%20Maka%20Naka%20Plastic%20campaign.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20life%2C%20Khandelwal%20shares%20that%20he%20has%20been%20dedicated%20to%20sustainability%20and%20mentoring.%20He%20is%20driven%20to%20establish%20practical%20ecosystems%20that%20support%20sustainable%20initiatives.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20founded%20Sensible%20Earth%2C%20the%20centre%20for%20sustainability%2C%20in%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20Sensible%20Earth%20serves%20as%20an%20incubator%20for%20sustainability-focused%20initiatives%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20emphasis%20on%20strengthening%20local%20ecosystems%2C%20reducing%20waste%2C%20and%20creating%20solutions%20for%20upcycling%20and%20recycling.%20Some%20prominent%20initiatives%20under%20his%20leadership%20include%20the%20%23makanakaplastic%20campaign%20and%20Zeroposro.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20began%20in%20the%20Philippines%2C%20where%20he%20received%20his%20education%20before%20studying%20business%20management%20at%20Boston%20University.%20Despite%20early%20internships%20with%20major%20consulting%20firms%2C%20he%20says%20he%20always%20maintained%20an%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018-19%2C%20Khandelwal%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20solo%20journey%20on%20his%20Triumph%20Tiger%20motorcycle%2C%20exploring%20India%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20Morocco.%20During%20this%20adventure%2C%20he%20encountered%20the%20profound%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297512%2Findian-farmers-agroforestry-climate-change-solution-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenges%20of%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20these%20regions.%20He%20says%20these%20experiences%20deeply%20affected%20him%2C%20inspiring%20him%20to%20take%20action%20rather%20than%20simply%20lamenting%20the%20issues.%20This%20pivotal%20moment%20led%20him%20to%20relocate%20to%20Goa%20and%20establish%20Sensible%20Earth%20as%20a%20means%20to%20make%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBags-and-other-products-made-from-pre-loved-fabric.-Photo-by-Arti-Das_11zon-1697030387-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cloth%20bags%20and%20other%20products%20hand-stitched%20from%20pre-loved%20fabric.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBags-and-other-products-made-from-pre-loved-fabric.-Photo-by-Arti-Das_11zon-1697030387-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBags-and-